    <p id="header">
        About Diabetes@Home<br />
        An online diabetes management tool for both patients and clinicians.
    </p>
    <p id="intro">
        Nowadays, the healthcare industry has undergone profound changes due to
        the impact of the ongoing global pandemic. This web app has been built
        up for easier access and monitoring patients' health status remotely,
        for both patients and clinicians, as well as providing a great platform
        for clinicians to giving the latest health advice to their patients in a
        more smooth and convenient way.<br /><br />
        You need to login to your account to get access to our services. For
        people with diabetes or those who need blood glucose monitoring, you can
        easily access our services anywhere through different devices, no matter
        you wish to use your handheld, tablet, or access from your PC.
    </p>
