<div class="content">
    <div class="text">
        <p class="heading">For patients</p>
        <p class="paragraph">
            You can get your account by contacting your clinician. After login
            you can log your daily data about blood sugar and activity data, and
            hence to analysis your recent trend. Different data categories might
            be required by your clinicians depending on your health status.
            Supports will also be easier to be accessed. Patients will receive
            messages from their clinicians when needed. Patients are also
            encouraged to be engaged with the application. You will be getting
            digital badge if you are being engaged and a leaderboard will show 5
            patients who have the highest engagement rate.<br /><br />
        </p>
        <p class="heading">For clinicians</p>
        <p class="paragraph">
            If you are a physician, you can provide your own credentials and log
            up as a clinician. You can get an overview of your patients in the
            dashboard, and click on a patient to see his or her details. You can
            also provide safe ranges based on patients' recent data and send
            messages to your patients.<br /><br />
        </p>
